description: Stendörren Fastigheter AB engages in owning, developing, and managing real properties. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 54 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2011-02-04. The company owns, manages and develops warehousing, industrial and office properties in the Stockholm region. The company invests in real estate with development potential, such as underlying rental value, partial vacancy or development rights. Its portfolio comprises more than 25 properties with a total space of around 260,000 square meters. The properties are located in Stockholm, Upplands Vasby, Taby, Jarfalla, Sigtuna, Upplands-Bro and Knivsta. The firm is also engaged in the development of logistics projects.
name: Stendorren Fastigheter AB
